Businesses in Komi are ready to lease cone dryer and greenhouses

01 Nov 2019, 09:43

The republic has expanded the list of property to support small and medium-sized enterprises.


Photo by Victor Bobyr

The new edition of the Regional Ministry of Property and Land Relations approved a list of state property provided on preferential terms to small and medium-sized enterprises.
The list includes 128 objects, including 122 buildings (premises), 3 land plots and 3 units of movable property. Lists are also compiled in the Komi municipalities (a total of 814 objects of municipal property).
Property is leased to small and medium-sized enterprises on preferential terms for a period of at least five years, without a bidding process. The measure of property support is provided in the framework of the national project “Small and medium-sized enterprises and the development of entrepreneurial initiative”.
The list is available on the official website of the Komi Ministry of Property in the section “Property support for small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs)”.
So, the list additionally includes 14 objects:
- three rooms in the office building (Izhemsky district, Izhma village, Chuprova street, 114);
- the building of a cone dryer (Kortkeros district, village Kortkeros, stantsionnaya st., 15b);
- building a garage for four cars (Kortkeros district, village of Storozhevsk, Misha Yag town);
- building (Priluzsky district, village of Obyachevo, village of Kuliga);
- office building of the leshoz (Pechora district, Kadzher st., Internationalnaya st., 18a);
- two buildings (Syktyvdinsky district, metro station Maksimovka);
- warehouse-hangar (Sysolsky district, village of Vizinga, Zelenaya St.);
- garage (Troitsko-Pechora district, White Bor village);
- land for agricultural use (Syktyvdinsky district, in the northwestern part of the cadastral quarter);
- a block of film greenhouses (movable property) (Kortkeros district, village Kortkeros);
- greenhouse (movable property) (Troitsko-Pechora district, White Bor village).
